{"generation_id":"gen_base_aflily_a8e987e7","status":"IN_QUEUE","input_text":"The low hum of the fluorescent lights mingled with the distant murmur of voices, a familiar symphony of eager searching. My teal plastic shell felt cool and solid in his hand, a small beacon amidst the crowded shelves. There was a faint scent of old electronics, a comforting dustiness in the air of this treasure trove. His thumb rested gently on my D-pad, the bright green “SD” sticker a recent addition, a personal touch. Though his face isn't fully in view, I remember the slight tilt of his head, his focus drawn to my dim, pixelated world. He wasn't just holding a device; he was rediscovering a piece of his own history, a quiet, personal moment within the bustling market. Around us, a collection of forgotten consoles and vibrant game boxes whispered tales of past adventures. This shared passion connected him not just to me, but to others unseen, a silent understanding. This moment, so simple, felt profound. Soon, the day would shift, and lives would continue, but this small spark of connection to a cherished past, that would forever remain, etched into the quiet corners of memory.","voice_id":"af_lily","voice_name":"Lily","model":"base","tokens":275,"dollar_cost":0.00275,"method":null,"audio_url":null,"error_message":null,"created_at":"2026-03-16T08:05:53.601754","started_at":null,"completed_at":null}